Service file
/etc/systemd/system/name_of_the_file.service                                                # create Service file at that location


Include these lines in name_of_the_file.service file

[Unit]
Description=My test service
After=multi-user.service

[Service]
Type=simple
Restart=always
ExecStart=/usr/local/bin/name_of_the_file.sh

[Install]
WantedBy=multi-user.target

In command terminal run this command

sudo cat /etc/systemd/system/name_of_the_file.service



